{"tid":570701,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[健康jj]有冇邊啲supplement 係又平質素又ok??","createTime":"2018-02-24T02:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T11:21:15.000Z","uid":95641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cde8d0421c70e17287e55b32be757d18c0339b92","tid":570701,"uid":95641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"小弟有啲閒錢想買啲supplement 食下，改善下身體，都有了解過市面上一啲專門賣supplement 嘅公司，但好多都係價錢偏貴/傳銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問有冇巴絲食開啲又平又真係可以改善到健康嘅supplement <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbd2a1844dd41e9c817c7e931a70f9c81c46a71","tid":570701,"uid":10608,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"改善健康就從飲食運動開始啦<br />\n乜染都十P文<br />\n十你老母臭系咩"},{"pid":"cb0af4ec74717376c7434f30454b838b9849e448","tid":570701,"uid":32380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:52:03.000Z","msg":"入嚟前以為打手"},{"pid":"acc348cba037b95eb49b57a8dc9c9b91c108f2bc","tid":570701,"uid":95641,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8fbd2a1844dd41e9c817c7e931a70f9c81c46a71","tid":570701,"uid":10608,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"改善健康就從飲食運動開始啦<br />\n乜染都十P文<br />\n十你老母臭系咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:06:39.000Z","msg":"鬼唔知阿媽係女人，你問十個香港人，有幾多個有時間可以長期keep住運動同健康飲食？<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知要由飲食改變健康要花幾多時間？淨係諗食咩、係邊度買食材、烹調方法...都用你大半日時間啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有，學好啲中文先嚟話人啦<br />\n又「染」又「系」都唔知你噏乜"},{"pid":"6c27deb751ce17985f21d97d8ec0548628ba4d91","tid":570701,"uid":95641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb0af4ec74717376c7434f30454b838b9849e448","tid":570701,"uid":32380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T02:52:03.000Z","msg":"入嚟前以為打手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:19:25.000Z","msg":"就係比傳銷搵過笨所以先係度問<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n集思廣益"},{"pid":"7f355060b4e1fb569e596918281101882569b9e3","tid":570701,"uid":154131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:40:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62edfc1a3f86e13e6188f46bc3281f8af7759cd6","tid":570701,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:56:17.000Z","msg":"運動運動同運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個西方醫學養生之道都係運動、重訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 配合健康飲食<br />\n<br />\n你唔信都冇計，一係信中醫個套，食藥調節身體加打大極，陰陽平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148a368513aea20272f7120bb33b16236017e2f6","tid":570701,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62edfc1a3f86e13e6188f46bc3281f8af7759cd6","tid":570701,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:56:17.000Z","msg":"運動運動同運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成個西方醫學養生之道都係運動、重訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 配合健康飲食<br />\n<br />\n你唔信都冇計，一係信中醫個套，食藥調節身體加打大極，陰陽平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T03:56:37.000Z","msg":"太極"},{"pid":"052b328aa0d4526c975b615f68496fe29dc22375","tid":570701,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"無人知，食20年先有效果"},{"pid":"b20ec35fd452f7a68198c17449fc31ff45aa9952","tid":570701,"uid":77473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T04:19:33.000Z","msg":"Supplement 部份都冇用 正常飲食就夠 <br />\n頂龍亞洲人食唔夠 Vita B and 鐵<br />\n<br />\n我嘅建議係二寶同食多啲肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4559eba0257cf0e5653c4c522e56e0a9571a1a41","tid":570701,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201